    <mxCell id="cmbody" value="Contracts at every boundary, with explicit validation logic, and orchestration-level awareness of what constitutes a valid system state at each stage. No failure mode listed above is a model capability problem. All four are contract and observability gaps. A system with complete contracts and runtime validation at every boundary will surface all four failure modes within minutes — not eleven days later." style="rounded=1;arcSize=2;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#CBD8EF;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#333D4D;" vertex="1" parent="1">
